Spark DataFrame Actions
-----------------------

Viewing Actions
---------------

Action              Purpose

show()              Display rows
head()              First row
first()             First row
take()              First N rows

Collecting Actions
------------------

Action              Purpose

collect()           Return all rows
toLocalIterator()   Iterator of rows

Counting Actions
----------------

Action      Purpose
count()     Count rows

Writing Actions
---------------

Action              Purpose
write.csv()         Write CSV
write.parquet()     Write Parquet
write.json()        Write JSON
write.orc()         Write ORC
write.jdbc()        Write DB

Other Actions
-------------

Action                  Purpose

foreach()               Apply function
foreachPartition()      Apply per partition
describe()              Summary statistics
summary()               Extended summary





















